Interface LinkDatasetGraphAccess

All Superinterfaces:
AutoCloseable, org.apache.jena.sparql.core.Transactional
All Known Subinterfaces:
LinkDatasetGraph, RDFLink
All Known Implementing Classes:
RDFLinkAdapter, RDFLinkDataset, RDFLinkFuseki, RDFLinkHTTP, RDFLinkModular
public interface LinkDatasetGraphAccess extends org.apache.jena.sparql.core.Transactional, AutoCloseable
SPARQL 1.1 Graph Store HTTP Protocol (read operations) and whole dataset access. LinkDatasetGraph extends this interface, and adds the write operations.
